'''Krish''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Krish (species)/Legends|Krish]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Sanza]]. Most Krish were fluent in both Krish and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although only literate in their own language. Krish was formed of grunts, bellows and crude vocalizations. The language also had a [[Written Krish|written form]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

